{"featured_counts":11,"common_counts":234,"collapsed_counts":1,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/563758139/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=57\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/563758139/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=55\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":108},"data":[{"id":568410633,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/568410633","content":"大家别责怪他了，他其实一直幻想着证明数学十大难题，高中没毕业就辍学了，然后一直待在家里，名字我不想暴露。今年都快三十岁了吧，希望他好好生活别再沉迷解决这些数学幻想了。他还有一堆其他数学难题的证明，而且相当自信自己解决了。字写得比较烂，像个小学生的字。这孩子还是没救了，不过已经是快三十岁的大孩子了\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e他爸天天骂他说他高中辍学后天天整这些有的没的，也不知道工作。他现在连自理生活的能力都没有了，以前一直和我对话说让我帮他投稿，没想到他证明都是这么低级的。哎!和新闻报道的那个哈工大沉迷解决歌猜，大学毕业证都没拿到，后来靠救济金过活，民科数论害了他。他不是什么营销号，希望他好好做人，好好生活。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e他是靠自学的，家里条件是比较好的，家里还是摆了一堆书的，不光靠瞎想的，有点小聪明，但是和社会脱节，也不怎么和别人接触，也不接触最前沿数论论文。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e之所以提这个问题是因为他没上过大学，也是想借这个机会一举成名，去上大学，他手上还有很多证明。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546281328,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"6305352e8d29f6d3539802bf432d6b73","url_token":"kim-young-71","name":"Tracker","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ca29a2d8d4bac3ec562a2966e60eb022_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ca29a2d8d4bac3ec562a2966e60eb022_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/6305352e8d29f6d3539802bf432d6b73","user_type":"people","headline":"大数据架构师","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false}},